      "announcement_url": null,
      "experiment_goals": "Our intent is to run a Finch experiment on 1% Stable instead of Origin Trials, because this feature is only exposed with heuristics and it doesn't have an API surface.\n\nWe run the experiment to evaluate the potential impact of ServiceWorkerAutoPreload on the loading metrics. And also we’d like to gather input and feedback for the reasonable criteria, or conditions to enable ServiceWorkerAutoPreload when it’s fully launched.\n\nConversely, currently we don’t have a plan to ship this feature as it is without any criteria or conditions. ",
